  <span id="freeText11661071247802808906" style="display:none">Good read. I really liked parts of this book, while others I wish were a little different! There's a great mystery hidden within that will continue (I hope) through the series. Many questions come up as you read about these characters and only some are answered! So of coarse I MUST go on! :D There were definite lulls in the pace however. Sometimes I wished some scenes were shorter or not quite as well described and detailed. And there was one time when I felt it was repeating a scene a little.... However the characters are highly interesting and the sub characters are even more so! I can't wait for some of their stories and to see what happens with them! Especially since I'm still not sure where one characters loyalty truly lies! ;) <br /><br />Songs: "Tell Your Heart to Beat Again" by Danny Gokey and "Press On" by Mandisa<br />Songs etc. May be changed and/or added in the future. ~ASC<br /><br />Psalm 51:10<br /><br />~ASC<br /><br />*I requested and received this book as a member of Litfuse for the purpose of reviewing it. This in no way affected my opinion and the above are my true thoughts and feelings about The Loyal Heart. ~ASC<br /><br /><a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="http://litfusegroup.com/author/sgray">http://litfusegroup.com/author/sgray</a></span>
